name: brucella-phylo
channels:
  - conda-forge
  - bioconda
  - defaults
dependencies:
  - python=3.11
  - snippy
  - gubbins
  - iqtree2
  - snp-sites
  - mafft            # if you ever realign anything
  - biopython        # for any small scripts
  - pandas           # optional, for tables
  - matplotlib       # optional, for quick plots


snippy from bioconda.

gubbins from bioconda.
​

iqtree2 is the v2 binary (installed via iqtree2 package).
​

snp-sites from bioconda for core-SNP extraction.
